ffi::os_str::OsString::clear.doc:
Truncates the `OsString` to zero length.

# Examples

```
use std::ffi::OsString;

let mut os_string = OsString::from("foo");
assert_eq!(&os_string, "foo");

os_string.clear();
assert_eq!(&os_string, "");
```

